<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:32:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人类真的可以离开地球吗？ 【星际飞船】</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-humans-really-leave-earth-interstellar-spaceship</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-humans-really-leave-earth-interstellar-spaceship</guid></item><item><title>PI3K 亚型在 PTEN 缺陷的胶质母细胞瘤中的不同作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas</link><description>（细胞报告&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/divergent-roles-of-pi3k-isoforms-in-pten-deficient-glioblastomas</guid></item><item><title>前大学运动员与运动相关的头部暴露特征和健康结果CARE 联盟研究</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/sport-related-head-exposure-characteristics-and-health-outcomes-in-former-collegiate-athletesa-care-consortium-study</link><description>前大学运动员与运动相关的头部暴露特征和健康结果：一项 CARE 联盟研究。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sport-related-head-exposure-characteristics-and-health-outcomes-in-former-collegiate-athletesa-care-consortium-study2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 12:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/sport-related-head-exposure-characteristics-and-health-outcomes-in-former-collegiate-athletesa-care-consortium-study</guid></item><item><title>对成人胸腺健康的影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/thymic-health-consequences-in-adults</link><description>评估胸腺功能和健康突显了胸腺作为一种可以改善健康结果、预防疾病和促进健康老龄化的器官的终生重要性。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/thymic-health-consequences-in-adults2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/thymic-health-consequences-in-adults</guid></item><item><title>热激后通读转录过程中 CPSF73 激活和 3&amp;#39; RNA 聚合酶 II 暂停丢失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cpsf73-activation-and-3%e2%80%b2-rna-polymerase-ii-pausing-are-lost-during-readthrough-transcription-after-heat-shock</link><description>在这里，我们确定了热休克改变的转录终止机制的关键特征，从而能够全面读取 mRNA 基因的 3&amp;#39; 端。 Pol II 3&amp;#39; 暂停丢失，Ser2 和 Tyr1 处的 CTD 磷酸化发生变化，转录本的核酸内切裂解受损，但通过裂解激活剂 RBBP6 的表达可以缓解这种情况。我们的数据支持应激期间的多方面通读机制，即 Pol II 和终止机制的变化会触发转录绕过正常终止位点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cpsf73-activation-and-3e280b2-rna-polymerase-ii-pausing-are-lost-during-readthrough-transcription-after-heat-shock2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cpsf73-activation-and-3%e2%80%b2-rna-polymerase-ii-pausing-are-lost-during-readthrough-transcription-after-heat-shock</guid></item><item><title>衰老处于产后重塑和肿瘤发生的十字路口</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/senescence-at-the-crossroads-of-postpartum-remodeling-and-tumorigenesis</link><description>细胞衰老与有益和有害的功能有关。 Chiche、Djoual、Charifou 及其同事表明，衰老支持正常的产后乳腺重塑，但当致癌事件与退化同时发生时，衰老细胞通过调节可塑性、侵袭和转移来增强肿瘤发生。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/senescence-at-the-crossroads-of-postpartum-remodeling-and-tumorigenesis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/senescence-at-the-crossroads-of-postpartum-remodeling-and-tumorigenesis</guid></item><item><title>芯片上的人类神经元如何学会玩《毁灭战士》</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-human-neurons-on-a-chip-learned-to-play-doom</link><description>Cortical Labs 表示，这一特技指向一种新型的低功耗计算，或许也是一种研究神经药物的新方法&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-human-neurons-on-a-chip-learned-to-play-doom.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-human-neurons-on-a-chip-learned-to-play-doom</guid></item><item><title>人工智能设计的肽可以治愈……一切。 LigandForge 就在这里</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ai-designed-peptides-could-cure-everything-ligandforge-is-here</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 10:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ai-designed-peptides-could-cure-everything-ligandforge-is-here</guid></item><item><title>古代DNA在安纳托利亚发现了15,800年前的狗，它们的埋葬方式与人类一样</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans</link><description>利物浦大学/英国安卡拉研究所在土耳其安纳托利亚中部的两个考古发掘项目中发现了一些最早的狗的证据。研究结果记录在《早期家犬的发展和传播》中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ancient-dna-finds-15800-year-old-dogs-in-anatolia-buried-like-humans</guid></item><item><title>《黑客帝国》：谁真正扮演尼奥？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-matrix-who-was-actually-playing-as-neo</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-matrix-who-was-actually-playing-as-neo</guid></item></channel></rss>